cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting phy_log_level to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors during gNB initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 phy_log_level 設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid' 會在 gNB 初始化期間導致配置解析錯誤。
